# {{lb|en|transitive}} To use a knife to [[injure]] or [[kill]] by [[stab]]bing, [[slash]]ing, or otherwise using the sharp edge of the knife as a [[weapon]].
# {{lb|en|intransitive}} To cut through as if with a knife.
# {{lb|en|transitive}} To [[betray]], especially in the context of a [[political]] [[slate]].
# {{lb|en|transitive}} To positively [[ignore]], especially in order to [[denigrate]]. compare [[cut]]

